  "texts": [
    "It is unsurprising that LMs can leverage additional metadata to infer latent clusters.",
    "A natural question is whether LMs can also infer such metadata on their own.",
    "To investigate this, we introduce five new meta tokens, <s1> through <s5>.",
    "These tokens do not exist in the original vocabulary and are prepended to each sequence with probability 0.9, enclosed by <boc> and <eoc>.",
    "As all the prepending runs, we mask out the meta token loss for backpropagation."
  ],
  "correct_citations": []
}